		<h5>Introduction:</h5>

		<h5>How to Get Started</h5>

		<p>
			<ol>
				<li>Go to the app store and download the app <em>Shower-Busters</em>.

				<li>Once downloaded, open the app and wait for it to load.

				<li>When you see a page with a button that says start and instructions on it, you are in the right place.

				<li>Click on the instrctions button and read through how to play.

				<li>Once you have the instructions go back to the start page and click the button that says play.

				<li>That should take you to a calender.

				<li>If it is your first time playing click Day 1, otherwise click the day you are on.

				<li>If you click Day 1, there will be a page that has a timer on it.

				<li>When you are ready to take a shower click start and take a regular shower.

				<li>When you are done make sure to press stop.


				<li>Next time you take a shower click the following day.

				<li>Now the screen will tell you a shower time goal.

				<li>The timer will read how long it took you to take a shower on Day 1.

				<li>Start the timer and once again take a shower.

				<li>To earn the highest amount of points, end your shower before the timer runs out.

				<li>If you get out of the shower right when the timer goes off, you will earn the second highest amount of points.

				<li>If are not finished when the timer goes off and have to stay in the shower longer, you will earn the least amount of points.

				<li>Each time you take a shower you will click the next day and the timer will decrease by one minute until you reach you goal.</li>
			</ol>
